Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:17:58.85,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔戈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:06.55,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:33.44,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:44.29,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.11,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:51.25,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:12.83,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我作弊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:15.23,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:18.02,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是发挥了你自己的个性而已
